---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<Layout lang={lang} title="Privacy Policy — IP Consulting" description="How we collect, use, and protect your personal data.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: January 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">1. Data Controller</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          [Consultant Name] ("we", "us", or "our") operates this website. For data protection inquiries, contact us at: <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">contact@example.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">We collect the following categories of data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Contact data:</strong> Name and email address submitted via our lead capture form.</li>
          <li><strong>Booking data:</strong> Name, email, and scheduling information submitted via Cal.com.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages visited, time on site, and referral sources (via analytics cookies, only if consented).</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We process your data on the basis of your consent (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR) when you submit the lead capture form or accept cookies, and on the basis of a pre-contractual relationship (Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR) when you book a consultation.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">4. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li>To send you the requested downloadable resource.</li>
          <li>To schedule and confirm consultations.</li>
          <li>To send periodic insights and updates (only with explicit consent).</li>
          <li>To improve our website performance and user experience.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We retain personal data for no longer than necessary for the purposes described above, or as required by law. Contact data is deleted within 24 months of last interaction unless a contractual relationship exists.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data.</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time.</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict processing.</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with your local supervisory authority.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, contact: <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">contact@example.com</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">7. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We use strictly necessary cookies for site functionality and, with your consent, analytics cookies to understand how visitors interact with this website. You may withdraw consent at any time by clearing your browser cookies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We use Cal.eu for scheduling (subject to their Privacy Policy). We may use an email service provider for newsletter distribution. No data is sold to third parties.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-navy font-medium hover:text-gold transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18"/></svg>
        Back to home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
